{"tid":1543910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"831 太子警察插贓嫁禍","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T10:21:01.000Z","uid":232463,"like":116,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"c771693794cf4e601e91d5268b4e1c5a2740b1a0","tid":1543910,"uid":232463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"我係831嘅目擊者 <br />\n我見到有兩個係我面前比速龍拉<br />\n我影低左佢地被捕嘅過程<br />\n然後再遂格遂格睇翻先發現左樣野<br />\n條片入面有兩名被捕者<br />\n你會見到右手面跌左個豬嘴落黎<br />\n之後就有隻狗走去右面執起左<br />\n然後放左去左手面果位白色衫到<br />\n我唔知道最後左手面嘅手足比人告乜野罪<br />\n但係如果佢地因爲一個豬嘴而告你暴動嘅話<br />\n希望呢條片可以幫到你<br />\n<br />\n仲有我記得果陣仲有個比防暴叉頸果個車廂嘅男仔 希望你可以去提告 因為成個過程中佢地冇打我淨係用胡椒噴霧凶我入車廂 所以佢比起我會更有力<br />\n<br />\nPS 呢個連登ac我係問朋友借<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TtUux1kgkeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTtUux1kgkeE&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=5a6d065f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TtUux1kgkeE</a>"},{"pid":"434482ebf5970abc32b0a6c7203bbead60fdb8fd","tid":1543910,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:10:24.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud9tv0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd9tv0z.jpg&h=17d13451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumb